name: Louis The Child At Red Rocks (Ticket Lottery)
description: Once the NFT is sold out, one lucky winner will be selected to attend this show in person at Red Rocks in Morrison, Colorado. Winners will be selected randomly (using excel) and announced on my twitter @concertX. Once we receive a tweet from you claiming the prize, the ticket will then be transferred into your email. Trust the process, it's 1 TEZ.
